Decentralization is the founding principle of crypto currency and its strength lies in the power of the collective. As individuals we can only go so far. As a community of Pulsators we offer an opportunity to succeed together. Our token is meant to give an opportunity to take part in a larger passive income stream. With the launch of Pulse Chain just around the corner we are setting ourselves up to be a first mover in the space and look forward to Pulsating with each and every one of you!
